<text><body>
<lb n="0802c02"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0802c03"/>
<lb n="0802c04"/><head type="no">No. 701</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0802c05"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><title><note n="0802007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【宮】＊</note><app n="0802007"><lem>佛說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>溫室洗浴眾僧經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0802c06"/>
<lb n="0802c07"/><byline type="Translator">後漢安息三藏安世高譯</byline>
<lb n="0802c08"/><p>阿難曰。吾從佛聞如是。一時佛在摩<note n="0802008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">竭＋（提）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0802008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">竭＋（提）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0802008"><lem>竭</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">竭提</rdg></app>國
<lb n="0802c09"/>因沙崛山中。王舍城內。有大長者。奈女之子。
<lb n="0802c10"/>名曰耆域。為大醫王。療治眾病。少小好學。
<lb n="0802c11"/>才藝過通。智達五經。天文地理。其所治者。莫
<lb n="0802c12"/>不除愈。死者更生。喪車得還。其德甚多。不
<lb n="0802c13"/>可具陳。八國宗仰。見者歡喜</p>
<lb n="0802c14"/><p>於是耆域。夜欻生念。明至佛所。當問我疑。
<lb n="0802c15"/>晨旦&CB00330;家大小眷屬。嚴至佛所。到精舍門。見
<lb n="0802c16"/>佛炳然。光照天地。眾坐四輩。數千萬人。佛
<lb n="0802c17"/>為說法。一心靜聽。耆域眷屬。下車直進。為
<lb n="0802c18"/>佛作禮。各坐一面</p>
<lb n="0802c19"/><p>佛慰勞曰。善來醫王。欲有所問。莫得疑難。
<lb n="0802c20"/>耆域長跪白佛言。雖得生世。為人&CB00520;野。隨
<lb n="0802c21"/>俗眾流。未曾為福。今欲請佛及<note n="0802009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔諸眾〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0802009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔諸眾〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0802009"><lem>諸眾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>僧菩
<lb n="0802c22"/>薩大士。入溫室澡浴。願令眾生長夜清淨穢
<lb n="0802c23"/>垢消除不遭眾患。唯佛聖旨。不忽所願</p>
<lb n="0802c24"/><p>佛告醫王。善哉妙意。治眾人病。皆蒙除愈。
<lb n="0802c25"/>遠近慶賴。莫<note n="0802010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＋（復）【三】</note><note n="0802010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不＋（復）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0802010"><lem>不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">不復</rdg></app>歡喜。今<note n="0802011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔復〕－【三】</note><note n="0802011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔復〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0802011"><lem>復</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>請佛及<note n="0802012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔諸眾〕－【宮】</note><app n="0802012"><lem>諸眾</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0802c26"/>僧。<note n="0802013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔入溫室〕－【宮】</note><app n="0802013"><lem>入<note n="0802014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔溫〕－【三】</note><note n="0802014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔溫〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0802014"><lem>溫</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>室</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>洗浴。願及十方眾藥療<note n="0802015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">病＝疾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0802015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">病＝疾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0802015"><lem>病</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">疾</rdg></app>。洗
<lb n="0802c27"/>浴除垢。其福無量。一心<note n="0802016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諦聽＝聽法【三】【宮】</note><note n="0802016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諦聽＝聽法【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0802016"><lem>諦聽</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">聽法</rdg></app>。吾當為汝先
<lb n="0802c28"/>說澡浴眾僧<note n="0802017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">反＝及【明】</note><app n="0802017"><lem>反</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">及</rdg></app>報之福。佛告耆域。澡浴之
<lb n="0802c29"/>法。當用七物除去七病。得七福報。何謂七
<pb ed="T" id="T16.0701.0803a" n="0803a"/>
<lb n="0803a01"/>物。一者然火。二者淨水。三者澡豆。四者
<lb n="0803a02"/><note n="0803001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蘇＝酥【元】【明】</note><app n="0803001"><lem>蘇</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">酥</rdg></app>膏。五者淳灰。六者楊枝。七者內衣。此
<lb n="0803a03"/>是澡浴之法。何謂除<note n="0803002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔去〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0803002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔去〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0803002"><lem>去</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>七病。一者四大安
<lb n="0803a04"/>隱。二者除風病。三者除濕痺。四者除寒&CB00457;。
<lb n="0803a05"/>五者除熱氣。六者除垢穢。七者身體輕便。眼
<lb n="0803a06"/>目精明。是為除<anchor id="fxT16p0803a01"/>去眾僧七病。如是供養。便
<lb n="0803a07"/>得七福。何謂七福。一者四大無病。所生常
<lb n="0803a08"/>安。勇武丁健。眾所敬仰。二者所生清淨。面
<lb n="0803a09"/><note n="0803003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">目＝貌【三】【宮】</note><note n="0803003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">目＝貌【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0803003"><lem>目</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">貌</rdg></app>端正。塵水不著。為人所敬。三者身體常
<lb n="0803a10"/>香。衣服潔淨。見者歡喜。莫不<note n="0803004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">恭＝欽【三】【宮】</note><note n="0803004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">恭＝欽【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0803004"><lem>恭</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">欽</rdg></app>敬。四者
<lb n="0803a11"/>肌體<note n="0803005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">濡＝潤【宮】</note><app n="0803005"><lem>濡</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">潤</rdg></app>澤。威光德大。莫不敬歎。獨步無雙。
<lb n="0803a12"/>五者多饒人從。拂拭塵垢。自然受福。常識
<lb n="0803a13"/>宿命。六者口齒香好。方白齊平。所說教令。
<lb n="0803a14"/>莫不<note n="0803006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">肅＝開【宮】</note><app n="0803006"><lem>肅</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">開</rdg></app>用。七者所生之處。自然衣裳光飾
<lb n="0803a15"/>珍寶。見者悚息</p>
<lb n="0803a16"/><p>佛告耆域。作此洗浴眾僧開士。七福如是。從
<lb n="0803a17"/>此因緣。或為人臣。或為帝王。或為日月四
<lb n="0803a18"/>天神王。或為帝釋<note n="0803007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（或為）＋轉【三】【宮】</note><note n="0803007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（或為）＋轉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0803007"><lem>轉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">或為轉</rdg></app>輪聖王。或<note n="0803008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＝為【三】【宮】</note><note n="0803008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">生＝為【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0803008"><lem>生</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">為</rdg></app>梵天。受
<lb n="0803a19"/>福難量。或為菩薩。發意<note n="0803009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">持＝治【三】【宮】</note><note n="0803009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">持＝治【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0803009"><lem>持</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">治</rdg></app>地。功成志就。遂
<lb n="0803a20"/>致作佛。斯之因<note n="0803010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">緣＝由【三】【宮】</note><note n="0803010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">緣＝由【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0803010"><lem>緣</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">由</rdg></app>。供養眾僧。無量福田。旱
<lb n="0803a21"/>澇不傷。於是世尊。重為耆域。而作頌曰</p>
<lb n="0803a22"/><lg><l>觀諸三界中</l><l>天人受<note n="0803011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">景＝影【宮】</note><app n="0803011"><lem>景</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">影</rdg></app>福</l>
<lb n="0803a23"/><l>道德無限量</l><l>諦聽次說之</l>
<lb n="0803a24"/><l><note n="0803012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夫＝天【元】</note><app n="0803012"><lem>夫</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">天</rdg></app>人生處世</l><l>端正人所敬</l>
<lb n="0803a25"/><l>體性常清淨</l><l>斯由洗眾僧</l>
<lb n="0803a26"/><l>若為大臣子</l><l>財富常吉安</l>
<lb n="0803a27"/><l>勇健<note n="0803013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">忠＝中【三】【宮】</note><note n="0803013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">忠＝中【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0803013"><lem>忠</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">中</rdg></app>賢良</l><l>出入無罣礙</l>
<lb n="0803a28"/><l>所說人奉用</l><l>身體常香潔</l>
<lb n="0803a29"/><l>端正色從容</l><l>斯由洗眾僧</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T16.0701.0803b" n="0803b"/>
<lb n="0803b01"/><l>若生天王家</l><l>生即常潔淨</l>
<lb n="0803b02"/><l>洗浴以香湯</l><l>苾芬以熏身</l>
<lb n="0803b03"/><l>形體與眾異</l><l>見者莫不欣</l>
<lb n="0803b04"/><l>斯造溫室浴</l><l>洗僧之福報</l>
<lb n="0803b05"/><l>第一四天王</l><l>典領四<note n="0803014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">方域＝域方【三】【宮】</note><note n="0803014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">方域＝域方【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0803014"><lem>方域</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">域方</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0803b06"/><l>光明身端正</l><l>威德護四鎮</l>
<lb n="0803b07"/><l>日月及星宿</l><l><note n="0803015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">光＝晃【三】【宮】</note><note n="0803015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">光＝晃【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0803015"><lem>光</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">晃</rdg></app>照除陰冥</l>
<lb n="0803b08"/><l>斯由洗眾僧</l><l>福報如影響</l>
<lb n="0803b09"/><l>第二忉利天</l><l>帝釋名曰因</l>
<lb n="0803b10"/><l>六重之寶城</l><l>七寶為宮殿</l>
<lb n="0803b11"/><l>勇猛天中尊</l><l>端正壽延長</l>
<lb n="0803b12"/><l>斯由洗眾僧</l><l>其報無等倫</l>
<lb n="0803b13"/><l>世間轉輪王</l><l>七寶導在前</l>
<lb n="0803b14"/><l>周行四海外</l><l>兵馬八萬四</l>
<lb n="0803b15"/><l>明寶照晝夜</l><l>玉女隨時供</l>
<lb n="0803b16"/><l>端正身香潔</l><l>斯由洗眾僧</l>
<lb n="0803b17"/><l>第六化應天</l><l>欲界中獨尊</l>
<lb n="0803b18"/><l>天相光影足</l><l>威靈震六天</l>
<lb n="0803b19"/><l>自然食甘露</l><l><note n="0803016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">妓＝伎【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0803016"><lem>妓</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">伎</rdg></app>女常在邊</l>
<lb n="0803b20"/><l>眾德難稱<note n="0803017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">譽＝喻【三】【宮】</note><note n="0803017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">譽＝喻【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0803017"><lem>譽</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">喻</rdg></app></l><l>斯由洗眾僧</l>
<lb n="0803b21"/><l>梵魔三&CB00425;天</l><l>淨居修自然</l>
<lb n="0803b22"/><l>行淨無垢穢</l><l>又無女人形</l>
<lb n="0803b23"/><l>梵行修潔己</l><l>志淳在泥洹</l>
<lb n="0803b24"/><l>得生彼天中</l><l>斯由洗眾僧</l>
<lb n="0803b25"/><l>佛為三界尊</l><l>修道甚苦勤</l>
<lb n="0803b26"/><l>積行無數劫</l><l>今乃得道真</l>
<lb n="0803b27"/><l>金體玉為瓔</l><l>塵垢不著身</l>
<lb n="0803b28"/><l>圓光相具足</l><l>斯由洗眾僧</l>
<lb n="0803b29"/><l>諸佛從行得</l><l>種種不勞勤</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T16.0701.0803c" n="0803c"/>
<lb n="0803c01"/><l>所施三界人</l><l>無<note n="0803018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">所＝處【三】【宮】</note><note n="0803018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">所＝處【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0803018"><lem>所</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">處</rdg></app>不周遍</l>
<lb n="0803c02"/><l>眾僧之聖尊</l><l>四道良福田</l>
<lb n="0803c03"/><l>道德從中出</l><l>是行最妙真</l></lg>
<lb n="0803c04"/><p>佛說偈已。重告耆域。觀彼三界。人天品類。
<lb n="0803c05"/>高下長短。福德多少。皆由先世用心不等。是
<lb n="0803c06"/>以所受各異。不同如此。受諸福報。皆由洗
<lb n="0803c07"/>浴聖眾得之耳。佛說經已。阿難白佛言。當何
<lb n="0803c08"/>名此經。以何勸誨之</p>
<lb n="0803c09"/><p>佛告阿難。此經名<note n="0803019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔曰〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0803019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔曰〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0803019"><lem>曰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>溫室洗浴眾僧經。諸
<lb n="0803c10"/>佛所說。非我獨造。行者得度。非神授與。求
<lb n="0803c11"/>清淨福。自當奉行。佛說<note n="0803020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔是〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0803020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔是〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0803020"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>經竟。耆域眷屬。
<lb n="0803c12"/>聞經歡喜。<note n="0803021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔皆〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0803021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔皆〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0803021"><lem>皆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>得須陀洹道。禮佛求退。嚴辦
<lb n="0803c13"/>洗具。眾坐大小。各得道<note n="0803022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00528;＝跡【三】【宮】</note><note n="0803022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00528;＝跡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0803022"><lem>&CB00528;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">跡</rdg></app>。皆共稽首。禮佛
<lb n="0803c14"/>而去</p>
<lb n="0803c15"/><trailer><anchor id="fxT16p0803c01"/><title>佛說溫室洗浴眾僧經</title></trailer><juan fun="close" n="001"></juan></div1>
